{"tid":2159261,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–武肺會否在急凍雞翼上大量繁殖","createTime":"2020-08-16T08:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T06:32:19.000Z","uid":38861,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f533245655aaa69725b479ca0b02efbcff4628f5","tid":2159261,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"近日有急凍雞翼及其他產品被測量出擁有武肺存在，但武肺能否在雞翼或其他食物上大量繁殖呢？<br />\n<br />\n答案是，不可以。<br />\n<br />\n武肺進行大量繁殖的話，必需要借助活生生的細胞幫忙，而其中先決的一步就是要進入細胞體內。<br />\n<br />\n武肺可否入侵細胞，基本上視乎可唔可以達成下列3個條件。<br />\n（圖1）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKBNfGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKBNfGF.jpg&h=ac84b902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. S protein與細胞表面的ACE2觸碰。<br />\n<br />\n2. 細胞表面ACE2與S protein的形狀吻合，亦即是「啱嘴形」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 細胞表面擁有TMPRSS2蛋白質，能夠對S protein進行切割。<br />\n<br />\n滿足3大條件後，病毒就有能力能夠入侵細胞。<br />\n當然，入侵細胞後還有很多因素決定武肺能否大量繁殖，但急凍雞翼連活生生的細胞也沒有，根本無可能可以大量繁殖。<br />\n<br />\n何謂S protein和ACE2，可到我之前所寫的文章溫故知新。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/issue/9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Fissue%2F9&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=4d82eb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/issue/9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rVVut1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrVVut1K.jpg&h=19fc0509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）<br />\n第二點所謂的「啱嘴型」，所指的就是ACE2的形狀能否與武肺的S protein形狀吻合，就好像砌Puzzle一樣，兩者不吻合的話就無法連結一起，勉強亦無幸福。<br />\n<br />\n如圖中所見，正因為老鼠ACE2唔啱嘴型，所以武肺無法引致老鼠患上肺炎等病徵，袁教授等人因此亦改用啱嘴型的倉鼠作為武肺的動物實驗模型。<br />\n<br />\n（Ref 1)有科學家嘗試將武肺打落豬、雞和鴨身上，最終無法在牠們的任何器官身上找到武肺，而且亦沒有出現任何病徵，因此斷定牠們並不會受到武肺感染。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAJ4hU7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAJ4hU7.png&h=b947860e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）<br />\n關於第三點，肺(Lung)及腎臟(Kidney)同樣擁有一定數量的ACE2及TMPRSS2（Ref2)，因此將會成為武肺的主要針對對象。<br />\n<br />\n而心臟(Heart) 同樣擁有一定數量的ACE2，某程度亦解釋了為何武肺患者康復後會被發現心臟出現異樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而男性器官睪丸(Testis)，亦是ACE2數量較多的器官（圖中沒有列出），所以，嗯......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=ee0074ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=aa0435d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科普資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/368/6494/1016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F368%2F6494%2F1016&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=c676cc38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/368/6494/1016</a><br />\n<br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S221323172030820X#fig1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS221323172030820X%23fig1&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=d297b303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S221323172030820X#fig1</a>"},{"pid":"2082f5f3702eecf350e111cc5eb84255a2301a5f","tid":2159261,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd22ef3000335525de766658af0079177f5239ba","tid":2159261,"uid":304660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:19:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11029c79ac8b40d4c3cf39b2ffb773e0f5ed269","tid":2159261,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔會凍死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a673ff88be59b0fdda535a9acf92bd8c3c4af6e","tid":2159261,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1947ffab3b52f3f83fd3ab961064f64f5fd18ee","tid":2159261,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"講咁多做咩，留番比啲會生食雞翼既師奶驚啦"},{"pid":"0076181fea4001a2e98d929d893da42deb7550f0","tid":2159261,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT